						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up near a well.</p>						

						<p>This <hi rend="bold">late record</hi> contains details of date, <hi rend="italic">viz.,</hi> <hi rend="bold">Pramāthin, Āvaṇi 15.</hi></p>						

						<p>It registers that the villagers of Agaram Pallāpuram <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Avubaḷammasamudram sold a piece of land for a well to Śēku Muśāmiyar, son of Śēkuā Alāvattiṉ.</p>						

						</summary>
